trends: There has been one other sighting in Live Oak
There were no other sightings in Live Oak on or around July 10th 1976
Summary: Triangle with windows on front two sides and six lights on the back side.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the front porch and looked up and this triangle was coming toward my house from the north to the south. It slowly passed overhead and almost hit the antenna on the roof. When it passed I went to the back yard to watch it some more but it was no where to be seen. I first noticed that a shadow was coming by and thought it was clouds at first. It was triangular that was pointing south. It maid no noise and slowly crossed the house. It made me feel tingly and light headed. I lost site of it when it went straight up and disappeared.
